description:
Today is all about one of the most amazing saxophone players that ever live, Michael Brecker. This line is from a video recorded in 1985 and features the well known jazz standard, Blue Bossa. Michael doesn't hold back here and this line is harmonically adventurous to say the least. Enjoy and smash that like button!
Here's the link to the source video of the performance this came from:
https://youtu.be/jRMRTdBbK7g
